<SUMMARY>
SUMMARY:

 Pursuant to the Federal Advisory Committee Act (Pub. L. No. 92-463), notice is hereby given of meetings of three
committees of the Administrative Conference of the United States: Committee on Rulemaking, Committee on Regulation,
and Committee on Governmental Processes. The meeting of the Committee on Governmental Processes is a rescheduling
of a meeting previously announced for December 2, 1994. 



</SUMMARY>
