Price to CV Comparisons 


In the instances noted above and where there was otherwise no matching home market or third country sale, we based FMV
on CV. We calculated CV based on the sum of the cost of materials, fabrication, general expenses, and U.S. packing cost.
We made all adjustments described in the COP section (except for the inclusion of VAT) in calculating CV. In accordance
