<DOCTITLE>Magnetek; Owosso, MI, Amended Certification Regarding Eligibility To Apply for NAFTA Transitional Adjustment
Assistance</DOCTITLE>


In accordance with Section 223 of the Trade Act of 1974 (19 USC 2273) the Department of Labor issued a Certification
Regarding Eligibility to apply for NAFTA-Transitional Adjustment Assistance on October 7, 1994 for workers of Magnetek
in Owosso, Michigan. The certification notice was published in the 

Federal Register

