for index options on many occasions, including periodic lists of the maximum size eligibility for AUTO-X. The
Phlx also notes that other exchanges permit the use of automatic order delivery and executions systems for index options.






The Exchange believes that the proposed rule change is consistent with Section 6(b) of the Act in general, and Section
