2. Any rule 12b-1 fees received by the Sponsor in connection with the distribution of Fund shares to the Trust
will be immediately rebated by the Sponsor to the Trustee. 
3. All Trust Series will be structured so that their maturity dates will be at least thirty days apart from one another.

4. Applicants will comply in all respects with the requirements of rule 14a-3, except that the Trust will not
restrict its portfolio investments to ``eligible trust securities.'' 
5. Shares of a Fund which are held by a Series of the Trust will be voted by the Trustee of the Trust, and the Trustee will
